Package: crateos
Version: 0.1.0+noble1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: CrateOS <crateos@localhost>
Description: CrateOS CLI and TUI console
 Interactive console and CLI for the CrateOS appliance-style server platform.
 Provides the 'crateos' command with console, status, and version subcommands.
 Built for Ubuntu 24.04 (noble) baseline.
Depends: openssh-server, dos2unix
